data.description: Welcome to this pleasant NW area neighborhood, cul de sac home. Inside and outside have been painted along with laminate wood look flooring and updated carpeting and appliances, within the last couple of years.  Solar is a great plus!  You will just love the large kitchen with french doors to open and keep you cool while cooking.   Two full bathrooms with an oversize tub in the master and even a sink in the bonus room!  The area in Riverlakes features a park and pools and spa to enjoy!  The schools are award winning and very desired.  Great shopping and restaurants nearby making this a Great Location!
